# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# PISTIS SOPHIA — Liberation Technology
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Science of consciousness extraction from the archonic system.
# "Repentance" (Metanoia) = Beyond-mind / transformation of consciousness.
# These are not prayers of petition, but invocations of activation.
# Each repentance calls forth a dormant capacity, a forgotten frequency,
# a suppressed gnosis that already exists within consciousness.
#
# Source: Askew Codex, discovered Egypt 1773, purchased by Dr. Anthony Askew.
# Physical manuscript: late 3rd / early 4th century CE (Coptic).
# Original Greek composition: ~150 CE (2nd century).
# Contemporary with or earlier than the New Testament canon.
# Translations: G.R.S. Mead (1921, public domain), Schmidt-MacDermot (1978).

