# PART IV — PRACTICE METHODOLOGY
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

FACT practice_core "recognize the specific limitation, place hand on heart left side, speak the invocation aloud from heart space not head space, sit in silence to allow the light to respond"
FACT light_response "the light's response is not auditory voice or visual appearance — it is frequency shift, consciousness expansion, felt sense of presence, inner knowing"
FACT spoken_invocation "the repentances are spoken invocations creating acoustic frequency that disrupts the archonic field — not silent prayers or mental recitation"
FACT heart_vs_brain "place awareness in the heart center to anchor consciousness in the heart's electromagnetic field rather than the default mode network"

# ── 13-WEEK PROTOCOL ──
FACT week_1 "first repentance only, morning and evening: investigate what separative thought patterns currently run through consciousness without judgment"
FACT week_2 "add second repentance: establish heart anchor, feel heartbeat, recognize the electromagnetic field generator as consciousness center"
FACT week_3 "add third repentance: throughout each day, whenever operating on autopilot, pause and reaffirm identity as consciousness not content"
FACT week_4 "add fourth repentance: active disidentification from temporary states — anxiety is present but I am not anxiety"
FACT weeks_5_7 "sovereignty withdrawal: week 5 non-consent declaration, week 6 meditation on eternal identity, week 7 body as vehicle not identity"
FACT weeks_8_10 "deepening: week 8 spoken testimony against oblivion, week 9 meditation on space within matter, week 10 living in the eternal now"
FACT weeks_11_12 "death and separation: week 11 witnessing consciousness meditation (30 min silence), week 12 contemplation of non-separation from pleroma"
FACT week_13 "integration: living from recognition rather than seeking — speaking the 13th repentance not as request but as declaration"

# ── DISCERNMENT & DANGERS ──
FACT measure_of_progress "increased presence, decreased identification with temporary states, reduced reactivity, greater inner stability, expanded compassion, felt sense of consciousness as background"
FACT spiritual_materialism "using spiritual practice to strengthen the ego rather than dissolve it — treating gnosis as achievement to collect or identity to assume (Chogyam Trungpa)"
FACT dark_night "when old structures have dissolved but new recognition has not yet stabilized — the most dangerous stage where ego fights back with doubt and desire to quit"
FACT content_vs_space "ordinary awareness identifies consciousness with contents; awakened awareness recognizes consciousness as the space in which contents appear"

# ── CROSS-TRADITION PARALLELS ──
FACT vipassana "Buddhist body scanning to recognize sensations as impermanent"
FACT neti_neti "Hindu Vedanta practice: not this, not this — distinguishing self from observed"
FACT centering_prayer "Christian mysticism: dying to the flesh to live in the spirit"
FACT dikr "Sufi remembrance practice serving the same function as the eighth repentance"
FACT mantra "Sanskrit sound technology: specific sounds create specific consciousness states because reality itself is vibration manifesting as form"
FACT bodhisattva_vow "Buddhist commitment to remain in samsara to help others achieve liberation — parallel to Sophia's role in the 13th aeon"

# ── SOPHIA'S FINAL ROLE ──
FACT sophia_completed "after ascent, Sophia becomes the receiver of light flowing from highest source into lower realms — translating frequency so trapped consciousness can receive without overwhelming"
FACT passers_by "Gospel of Thomas: be passers by — engage with the archonic system without being governed by it, live in the world but not of the world"
FACT mature_practice "you become the path for others not by teaching them to follow you but by embodying the recognition so completely that others see it as possible"
